{"id":"6c24a235a14802d1c675c3042036069a70244003","url":"https://aiera.com.cn/2026/07/18/other/admin/104520/kimi-k3%ef%bc%8c%e5%85%a8%e7%90%83%e5%bc%80%e6%ba%90%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%80%ef%bc%81","title":"Kimi K3，全球开源第一！ – 新智元","site_name":"新智元","source":"新智元","byline":null,"excerpt":"新智元报道","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div>\n\t\t\t\n<h3>\n<section data-id=\"88402\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n<p><span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">&#160;&#160;</span></span></strong><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &#160;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</h3>\n<section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n<p><span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_3b253ef414-150.png\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\n</section>\n\n<p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx100h\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mro6i8k71zm8\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\">全球迄今为止最大的开源AI模型，正式上线！</span></span></p>\n<p><span mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1k46\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">昨夜，月之暗面（Moonshot AI）放出了其最新旗舰模型</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">Kimi K3，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">目标直指超越Claude/ChatGPT。</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1ohe\"><span textstyle=\"\">在前端代码竞技场，K3以1679分一举登顶，超越Claude Fable 5。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_4c832a09ef.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1drp\"><span textstyle=\"\">体验过的网友，直呼K3堪比Fable 5：</span></span></p>\n<section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\">要是把Kimi K3的名字换成 Fable 5，大家就会信它。</span></p>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\">但这不只是视觉层面的问题，功能上也是。两者都能达到同样的结果，但实现路径不同，但Kimi 的创意更强。</span></p>\n</section>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_060df41fab.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx168x\"><span textstyle=\"\">中国AI，又迎来另一个「DeepSeek时刻」！</span></span></p>\n<section data-mpa-action-id=\"mro74doam2u\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" data-mpa-template=\"t\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n\n<p data-mpa-action-id=\"mo9vocn01ahg\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mo9vocmtnmn\"><span textstyle=\"\">上下滑动查看</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n</section>\n<p data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://qzqs9kyge0.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=ODI4NzkxMzRhN2Q0ZTAyZTAzM2IxZThjMjMzY2U5ZTBfUHl0YXMwbHhmck9nUHJrdHowSzlkdjFHbTd6YUFIOFJfVG9rZW46T2pQNGJWcTBTb1VIanN4MzVxSGN5QzAzblZoXzE3ODQyNDY3Njc6MTc4NDI1MDM2N19WNA&add_watermark=true&scene_type=CCM\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38358458961474035\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1194\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"1194\" data-height=\"458\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505229728\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1bj2\"><span textstyle=\"\">Kimi K3现已登陆网页端、Kimi Work、Kimi Code和API，7月27日开放模型权重。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_0a593656c8.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_df9d89c9b2-147.png\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">K3：全球开源最大最强AI</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxzo5\"><span textstyle=\"\">K3是能力最强的Kimi模型:</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1oou\"><span textstyle=\"\">参数高达</span><span textstyle=\"\">2.8 万亿</span><span textstyle=\"\">，百万级上下文，原生多模态</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx9ng\"><span textstyle=\"\">架构基于自研的Kimi Delta Attention和 Attention Residuals；</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1x8h\"><span textstyle=\"\">注意力残差以低于2%的额外成本实现</span><span textstyle=\"\">~25%</span><span textstyle=\"\">的训练效率提升；</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1qyu\"><span textstyle=\"\">实现最高</span><span textstyle=\"\">6.3倍</span><span textstyle=\"\">解码加速。</span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxiru\"><span textstyle=\"\">它是全球首个开源的3T级模型，专为长时编程、知识工作和推理等前沿智能任务设计。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxxot\"><span textstyle=\"\">综合性能直逼Claude Fable 5 和 GPT 5.6 Sol。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxxot\"><span textstyle=\"\">在3大内部知识工作基准中，K3超越Claude Opus 4.8（max）与 GPT-5.5（xhigh）:</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_cf5c42026d.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxue2\"><span textstyle=\"\">这标志着 Kimi K3 在智能体知识工作能力上全面进化，实际应用更强大、更可靠。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1vth\"><span textstyle=\"\">在自我递归能力上，Kimi在技术报告中称，「K3与Fable-5（含潜在回退方案）达到了相近性能，但K3每次迭代的优化速度更快。」</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_43f4346b55.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx15s2\"><span textstyle=\"\">据网友Kai消息，Kimi已经用K3+Kimi Code来构建Kimi Code，AI自进化显现！</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_6fb90604b4.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1zkh\"><span textstyle=\"\">不止软件，甚至不止训练阶段，K3可以自己设计芯片和从零设计推理内核——</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_9499c690d0.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxosd\"><span textstyle=\"\">整体上，ArtificialAnalysis发布了对K3模型的评测，证实了Kimi K3的性能已经达到全球第三名！</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://qzqs9kyge0.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=Y2JmYWNiMjFmYTc0NjFkMzYyMzAyZDBlMzJhNWE1MDVfUE1OWTlMQ2dYd2Jua01ZcTF1SGZRYlN6QlpySTFzNXNfVG9rZW46VW10T2JGUncxbzF5a214cko1aGNGNmVCbkZoXzE3ODQyNDY3Njc6MTc4NDI1MDM2N19WNA&add_watermark=true&scene_type=CCM\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"4096\" data-height=\"1723\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505229684\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_b8c6d74ced.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_0fd7d26fd3.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://qzqs9kyge0.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=NDZiNWQzNDJiNTQ0MjdiOWFiZjU3NjcyN2ZiOGU5OGFfeU1WQVBxNDM3aVJ5ZmZsS0pSeGt5clZHaXRTVnRzTlRfVG9rZW46TE96YWJsNFZDb0lPcVR4SUFlZmNQOXY1bjhkXzE3ODQyNDY3Njc6MTc4NDI1MDM2N19WNA&add_watermark=true&scene_type=CCM\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5068027210884354\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1176\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"1176\" data-height=\"596\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505229739\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx24xx\"><span textstyle=\"\">Kimi坦承了与全球AI第一名和第二名的差距：</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_674ce78df5.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx2df\"><span textstyle=\"\">是时候重新选择了，你是选一个随时可能被封号的闭源的Claude Opus 4.8，还是选一个性能相当、价格更便宜的开源之王K 3?</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://qzqs9kyge0.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=ZjZjNGJjYmI4YjI1NGZiZWI2MWZhZWM4NzlkMWFjOTFfd3JFa1h4SmlsZnZUbFhnWmNUblJpQWxiaWlnczRtSXNfVG9rZW46Vkd6RWJINjhub1hySDB4QTV0c2NkN01WbmVtXzE3ODQyNDY3Njc6MTc4NDI1MDM2N19WNA&add_watermark=true&scene_type=CCM\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"804\" data-height=\"767\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505229686\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_e7822b8e7b.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_81ed7e5253.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_df9d89c9b2-147.png\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">实测惊人</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Kimi给每个人的Claude Opus</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n\n<section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\">K3实现了真正的「视觉闭环」：在代码和实时截图之间无缝迭代，即时查看并优化生成结果。</span></p>\n</section>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://qzqs9kyge0.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=YTc5MzM2ZmU5NTFiNjg3NTk0YmQ0MzY3MzU5OTFiNjNfaE91NEJtSFlNbGRnOXVUU1o3c3VRd3E5RWVOaVJ1ZElfVG9rZW46V0NVdWI0NjFhbzZtUWx4YlVqR2MwZ0FubkpjXzE3ODQyNDY3Njc6MTc4NDI1MDM2N19WNA&add_watermark=true&scene_type=CCM\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"640\" data-height=\"360\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505229692\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_b35fad03e6.gif\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_7a271dcb0b.gif\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"https://qzqs9kyge0.feishu.cn/space/api/box/stream/download/asynccode/?code=NDk0MzNhYzgwMGU0MmVkNDJiYzA0YmIxNGE0Yzg1YjlfNDlpMkFPNFJSN1NPM0NaQTVaTjBBa1RoQWoyZDhDQ1NfVG9rZW46QlVsRmJvZUNlb3JOR0x4bnBhTWNPZlRmbldjXzE3ODQyNDY3Njc6MTc4NDI1MDM2N19WNA&add_watermark=true&scene_type=CCM\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"\" usemap=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"640\" data-height=\"360\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505229743\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1ko6\"><span textstyle=\"\">有网友称，</span><span textstyle=\"\">Kimi K3是月之暗面的Mythos时刻</span><span textstyle=\"\">，在3D生成方面非常出色：</span></span></p>\n\n<section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\">在Three.js 中实现尼米兹级航空母舰上的战斗机起飞与回收</span></p>\n</section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxsip\"><span textstyle=\"\">网友实测，K3一句话就能做小游戏，CS、英雄联盟、炉石，都是K3一句话做出。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_117d1aedee.gif\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1i4k\"><span textstyle=\"\">在开发复古游戏上，据网友实测，Kimi K3以一半的成本击败了Opus 4.8。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_045ef49025.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1dnq\"><span textstyle=\"\">Kimi最出色的作品是 Q*bert，在该作品中，智能体能够改变立方体的状态、在金字塔上移动并躲避敌人，同时不破坏游戏循环。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_f547b03250.gif\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxgmc\"><span textstyle=\"\">一个提示词，15分钟，Kimi K3为AI操作系统构建了macOS风格的界面。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxc8n\"><span textstyle=\"\">在线投票显示，</span><span textstyle=\"\">Kimi K3在游戏开发领域击败Fable 5</span><span textstyle=\"\">，以87%的支持率绝对碾压过去被认为「全球最强AI」的Fable 5。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_ec2f9dc220.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1qi\"><span textstyle=\"\">Kimi K3绝对是AI发展史上的一个历史性时刻，开源AI进入后Claude Opus 4.8时代！</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_fcfd596268.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_df9d89c9b2-147.png\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">300亿美金豪赌</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">智能成为公共设施</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1hia\"><span textstyle=\"\">Kimi K3的2.8万亿总参数，是MoE架构的精妙设计——总参数巨大，但激活参数远低于总参数，提升了MoE的稀疏度，结合Stable LatentMoE 框架，实际推理时从 896 个专家中激活16个。</span></span></p>\n<section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_58eb1b1f3c.png\" alt=\"\"><br>\n  </section>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1x6i\"><span textstyle=\"\">配合优化后的训练策略与数据配比，这些结构改进使得整体扩展效率相比 Kimi K2 提升约 2.5 倍，让模型能更高效地将算力转化为智能。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1pju\"><span textstyle=\"\">当其他厂商还在用「参数规模」衡量模型时，K3已经用行动告诉我们：真正的竞赛，已经从「谁的参数更多」转向「谁的唤醒更聪明」。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhxl34\"><span textstyle=\"\">K2系列已采用Modified MIT许可开源权重，K3预计延续这一路径。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx167m\"><span textstyle=\"\">但目前，主要还是通过Kimi AI平台提供API访问，完整权重发布仍待官方进一步确认。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1scl\"><span textstyle=\"\">Bloomberg与SCMP确认，Moonshot AI在最新融资谈判中寻求约300亿美元估值，较此前数十亿美元实现指数级跃升。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1b43\"><span textstyle=\"\">资本市场为何如此看好？</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1qna\"><span textstyle=\"\">他们赌的，从来不是单一模型，而是中国AI「后发先至」的叙事本身：在资源约束下，以MoE架构实现高效规模化，以开放路径加速生态构建。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1n92\"><span textstyle=\"\">当一个中国公司把前沿能力推向全球时，AI竞赛的逻辑已从「零和博弈」转向「正和共生」。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1ohf\"><span textstyle=\"\">未来某天，全球开发者都能以极低成本调用接近顶级闭源模型的智能。</span></span></p>\n<p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mro6ikhx1f21\"><span textstyle=\"\">从此，智能不再是少数实验室的专利，而成为人类共同的「第二大脑」。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span leaf=\"\">https://www.kimi.com/blog/kimi-k3</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span leaf=\"\">https://x.com/testingcatalog/status/2077759985761554501</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span leaf=\"\">https://x.com/chetaslua/status/2077701096924229744</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span leaf=\"\">编辑：大卫</span></span></p>\n\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">秒追ASI</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">⭐</span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\">点赞、转发、在看一键三连</span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\">⭐</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n<section>\n   <span><strong><span leaf=\"\">点亮星标，锁定新智元极速推送！</span></strong></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n<p><span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_4d80689a0a-151.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span></p>\n<section>\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aiera.com.cn/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/aiera_img_50d0834dc7-18.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><br>\n  </section>\n\n\n\t\t</div></DIV>","content_text":"新智元报道 全球迄今为止最大的开源AI模型，正式上线！ 昨夜，月之暗面（Moonshot AI）放出了其最新旗舰模型Kimi K3，目标直指超越Claude/ChatGPT。 在前端代码竞技场，K3以1679分一举登顶，超越Claude Fable 5。 体验过的网友，直呼K3堪比Fable 5： 要是把Kimi K3的名字换成 Fable 5，大家就会信它。 但这不只是视觉层面的问题，功能上也是。两者都能达到同样的结果，但实现路径不同，但Kimi 的创意更强。 中国AI，又迎来另一个「DeepSeek时刻」！ 上下滑动查看 Kimi K3现已登陆网页端、Kimi Work、Kimi Code和API，7月27日开放模型权重。 K3：全球开源最大最强AI K3是能力最强的Kimi模型: 参数高达2.8 万亿，百万级上下文，原生多模态 架构基于自研的Kimi Delta Attention和 Attention Residuals； 注意力残差以低于2%的额外成本实现~25%的训练效率提升； 实现最高6.3倍解码加速。 它是全球首个开源的3T级模型，专为长时编程、知识工作和推理等前沿智能任务设计。 综合性能直逼Claude Fable 5 和 GPT 5.6 Sol。 在3大内部知识工作基准中，K3超越Claude Opus 4.8（max）与 GPT-5.5（xhigh）: 这标志着 Kimi K3 在智能体知识工作能力上全面进化，实际应用更强大、更可靠。 在自我递归能力上，Kimi在技术报告中称，「K3与Fable-5（含潜在回退方案）达到了相近性能，但K3每次迭代的优化速度更快。」 据网友Kai消息，Kimi已经用K3+Kimi Code来构建Kimi Code，AI自进化显现！ 不止软件，甚至不止训练阶段，K3可以自己设计芯片和从零设计推理内核—— 整体上，ArtificialAnalysis发布了对K3模型的评测，证实了Kimi K3的性能已经达到全球第三名！ Kimi坦承了与全球AI第一名和第二名的差距： 是时候重新选择了，你是选一个随时可能被封号的闭源的Claude Opus 4.8，还是选一个性能相当、价格更便宜的开源之王K 3? 实测惊人 Kimi给每个人的Claude Opus K3实现了真正的「视觉闭环」：在代码和实时截图之间无缝迭代，即时查看并优化生成结果。 有网友称，Kimi K3是月之暗面的Mythos时刻，在3D生成方面非常出色： 在Three.js 中实现尼米兹级航空母舰上的战斗机起飞与回收 网友实测，K3一句话就能做小游戏，CS、英雄联盟、炉石，都是K3一句话做出。 在开发复古游戏上，据网友实测，Kimi K3以一半的成本击败了Opus 4.8。 Kimi最出色的作品是 Q*bert，在该作品中，智能体能够改变立方体的状态、在金字塔上移动并躲避敌人，同时不破坏游戏循环。 一个提示词，15分钟，Kimi K3为AI操作系统构建了macOS风格的界面。 在线投票显示，Kimi K3在游戏开发领域击败Fable 5，以87%的支持率绝对碾压过去被认为「全球最强AI」的Fable 5。 Kimi K3绝对是AI发展史上的一个历史性时刻，开源AI进入后Claude Opus 4.8时代！ 300亿美金豪赌 智能成为公共设施 Kimi K3的2.8万亿总参数，是MoE架构的精妙设计——总参数巨大，但激活参数远低于总参数，提升了MoE的稀疏度，结合Stable LatentMoE 框架，实际推理时从 896 个专家中激活16个。 配合优化后的训练策略与数据配比，这些结构改进使得整体扩展效率相比 Kimi K2 提升约 2.5 倍，让模型能更高效地将算力转化为智能。 当其他厂商还在用「参数规模」衡量模型时，K3已经用行动告诉我们：真正的竞赛，已经从「谁的参数更多」转向「谁的唤醒更聪明」。 K2系列已采用Modified MIT许可开源权重，K3预计延续这一路径。 但目前，主要还是通过Kimi AI平台提供API访问，完整权重发布仍待官方进一步确认。 Bloomberg与SCMP确认，Moonshot AI在最新融资谈判中寻求约300亿美元估值，较此前数十亿美元实现指数级跃升。 资本市场为何如此看好？ 他们赌的，从来不是单一模型，而是中国AI「后发先至」的叙事本身：在资源约束下，以MoE架构实现高效规模化，以开放路径加速生态构建。 当一个中国公司把前沿能力推向全球时，AI竞赛的逻辑已从「零和博弈」转向「正和共生」。 未来某天，全球开发者都能以极低成本调用接近顶级闭源模型的智能。 从此，智能不再是少数实验室的专利，而成为人类共同的「第二大脑」。 参考资料： https://www.kimi.com/blog/kimi-k3 https://x.com/testingcatalog/status/2077759985761554501 https://x.com/chetaslua/status/2077701096924229744 编辑：大卫 秒追ASI ⭐点赞、转发、在看一键三连⭐ 点亮星标，锁定新智元极速推送！","fetched_at":"2026-07-19T06:56:27.304Z","ok":true}